    <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> ssh [SUNetID]@cardinal.stanford.edu
 cd /afs/ir.stanford.edu/group/alpslab/alpslab.stanford.edu
 git pull
</code></pre></div>    </div>

